name: Cheese Omelette Recipe | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Cheese Omelette Recipe: Eggs 4 Milk 3tbsp Salt ½ tsp Black pepper ½ tsp Cheddar cheese ½ cup Oil 6tbsp
instructions: In a bowl add eggs , salt , black pepper mix well. Now heat oil add eggs mixture cook on low flame for 4 to 5 min. Lastly add cheese on half omelet , fold and serve.
